column16: Ryan Doumit flies out to right fielder Jordan Danks.
Darin Mastroianni grounds into a double play, third baseman Jose Lopez to second baseman Orlando Hudson to first baseman Dan Johnson.   Drew Butera to 3rd.    Matt Carson out at 2nd.
Matt Carson walks.   Drew Butera to 2nd.
Drew Butera singles on a line drive to right fielder Jordan Danks.
Alex Rios grounds into a force out, shortstop Derek Jeter to second baseman Robinson Cano.    Adam Dunn out at 2nd.
Paul Konerko flies out to center fielder Curtis Granderson.
